  "body": "1. lblReplyMessage.height does not respect variable fontsize. Large font sizes can be truncated and small font sizes will leave extra spacing.\r\n2. The suspicious comment: `// childrenRect.height shows a binding loop for some reason, so we use heights instead`, it worth refactoring to use properties binding instead of height calculation as it is done right now.\r\n3. lblReplyMessage needs word wrapping + elide to be enabled. Plus, in according with the design we need to support \"expand\" button for long messages.",
